 Ghanaian President Nana Akufo-Addo has been presented with a customized Jersey of Real Madrid in Spain. Nana Addo Dankwah Akufo-Addo currently in Spain  for the “Focus Africa 2023” conference in Madrid, Spain. Spanish Prime Minister, Pedro Sánchez, today presented a customised Real Madrid jersey to President Akufo-Addo as his birthday present to the Ghanaian leader. The said jersey presented was autographed by several players of Real Madrid. President Akufo-Addo celebrated his 77th Birthday today,29th March 2021.